title: Qualified with April Beyer Episode 4
itunes:title: Qualified with April Beyer Episode 4
description:
Dating and relationship coach April Beyer is back as Anna’s co-host in another special episode. Their first call is with Amanda who wonders how and when to tell her boyfriend about her past struggles with an eating disorder. Next is a conversation with Megan who wonders if she should say anything about her younger sister’s new relationship with a much older family friend.


If you’re in need of unqualified relationship advice, please write to us at bit.ly/ASKANNA 


To learn more about April, go to https://aprilbeyer.com/site/meet-april/


Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
